00:10.868 --> 00:12.157
BETH ANN: I used to play the piano.

00:12.181 --> 00:14.031
- Do you still play?
- My husband...

00:14.056 --> 00:15.742
didn't care for my playing.

00:15.767 --> 00:18.382
Our daughter died because of me.

00:18.407 --> 00:20.784
I'm the one who's responsible.

00:20.809 --> 00:23.460
It seems I only have six months to live.

00:23.485 --> 00:24.625
[CRYING]: Six months!

00:24.650 --> 00:26.313
