01:22.214 --> 01:23.687
- Just give me the keys.
- Stop it.

01:23.712 --> 01:26.217
Go upstairs, get your stuff!

01:26.242 --> 01:29.101
I want you out of my house now!

01:29.126 --> 01:30.484
That's not gonna happen.

01:30.608 --> 01:31.945
How can I help?

01:31.977 --> 01:33.984
