49:23.680 --> 49:26.694
♪ I feel I've got to ♪

49:26.953 --> 49:29.999
♪ Run away, I've got to ♪

49:30.274 --> 49:32.381
♪ Get away from the pain ♪

49:32.406 --> 49:35.781
♪ You drive into the heart of me ♪

49:35.806 --> 49:38.434
♪ The love we share ♪

49:38.459 --> 49:41.913
♪ Seems to go nowhere ♪

49:41.938 --> 49:44.952
♪ And I've lost my light ♪

49:44.977 --> 49:49.311
♪ For I toss and turn,
I can't sleep at night ♪

49:49.757 --> 49:52.297
♪ Once I ran to you ♪

49:52.322 --> 49:53.499
♪ I ran ♪

49:53.524 --> 49:56.444
♪ Now I'll run from you ♪

49:56.469 --> 50:00.597
♪ This tainted love you've given,
I give you all ♪

50:00.622 --> 50:02.717
♪ A boy could give you ♪

50:02.742 --> 50:07.366
♪ Take my tears and
that's not nearly all ♪

50:07.391 --> 50:08.850
♪ Tainted love ♪

50:09.929 --> 50:12.123
♪ Tainted love ♪

50:13.372 --> 50:15.733
♪ Tainted love ♪

50:16.698 --> 50:18.529
♪ Tainted love ♪

50:18.554 --> 50:21.504
♪ Don't touch me, please ♪

50:21.529 --> 50:25.605
♪ I cannot stand the way you tease ♪

50:25.630 --> 50:28.186
♪ I love you though you hurt me so ♪

50:28.211 --> 50:31.294
♪ Now I'm gonna pack my things ♪

50:31.319 --> 50:33.115
- ♪ And go. ♪
- [GASPS]

